Class Slide

  • java.lang.Object
    • eclasstool.model.presentation.Slide

  • public class Slide
extends java.lang.Object
    The Slide is the implementation of a slide in a lecture A Slide is formatted in the Lecture Editor and viewed and presented in the Presentation Viewer.
